Connect to the 365 exchange

Add-MailboxPermission -Identity <MailboxIdentity> -User <UserIdentity> -AccessRights FullAccess -AutoMapping $false

Mailbox identity is whos mailbox it is. User Identity is who's going to have access to that mailbox
Remember to take out the <> too

For on the outlook app

Add-MailboxPermission -Identity "Terry Adams" -User "Kevin Kelly" -AccessRights FullAccess

This example assigns the user Kevin Kelly Full Access permission to Terry Adams's mailbox.
